# Format:
# type(scope): concise imperative summary
#
# Why:
# - business or technical reason
#
# What:
# - key behavior changes
#
# Validation:
# - npm run lint
# - npm run test

type(scope): describe the observable change

Why:
- explain why this change exists

What:
- summarize the important behavior or structure changes

Validation:
- npm run lint
